abstract: Gymnast Gabby Douglas wins American Cup in Newark.

headline.main: Victory Signals High Ambitions for Gabby Douglas

snippet: The reigning Olympic champion Gabby Douglas soared to victory in the American Cup in Newark, serving notice that she was ready to make another run at the podium in Rio de Janeiro this summer.
lead_paragraph: The reigning Olympic champion Gabby Douglas soared to victory in the American Cup in Newark, serving notice that she was ready to make another run at the podium in Rio de Janeiro this summer.
